Package: wallfetch
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: curl, wget
Description: Professional wallpaper fetching and management CLI tool
 WallFetch is a powerful command-line tool for fetching and managing
 wallpapers from various sources with intelligent duplicate detection
 and local library management.
 .
 Features:
  * Fetch wallpapers from Wallhaven and other sources
  * Intelligent duplicate detection using SHA256 checksums
  * Smart filtering by resolution, aspect ratio, and categories
  * Local database for metadata management
  * Concurrent downloads with configurable worker pools
  * Cross-platform support for Linux, macOS, and Windows 